commit.message:
config-list.mk (LIST): Add arm-rtems.

2014-09-18  Sebastian Huber  <sebastian.huber@embedded-brains.de>

	* config-list.mk (LIST): Add arm-rtems.
	Add nios2-rtems.  Remove extra option from powerpc-rtems.
